QuestData.Title: An Opened Can of Whoop Gnash
QuestData.Description: What an accomplishment, felling a mighty sea giant!$b$bThe new residents of Smuggler's Hole will feel considerably safer knowing this monster is no longer loitering outside their haven.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Gnash's Head to Samir in Smuggler's Hole.
QuestData.CompletionText: You took down that Sea Giant, $c?
QuestData.RewardText: It's not much, but it's all I've got down here.$b$bYou're more than welcome to it, $c.
